N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 251.12 - Certification of representatives

State Regulations

The board, upon the completion of its investigation, shall certify to the parties the name or names of the representatives selected, if any, or make other disposition of the matter. Notes
